700010f-a.title: Bronx: 3rd Avenue - 148th Street (East)
700010f-a.text:
Third Ave., north from East 148th Street, showing the Third Ave. Elevated Line structure thereon. In the foreground is the 149th Street station. Intersecting Third Ave., at this point, is Willis Ave.
May 1926.
Brown Brothers.
NWg W I04V
